==治療==
子宮內膜異位瘤可藉由手術治療，或是持續追蹤。藥物治療雖對於子宮內膜異位症有效果，但對於本病效果並無優於追蹤治療<ref>{{Cite journal|title=ESHRE guideline: management of women with endometriosis|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/24435778|last=Dunselman|first=G. a. J.|last2=Vermeulen|first2=N.|date=March 2014|journal=Human Reproduction (Oxford, England)|issue=3|doi=10.1093/humrep/det457|volume=29|pages=400–412|issn=1460-2350|pmid=24435778|last3=Becker|first3=C.|last4=Calhaz-Jorge|first4=C.|last5=D'Hooghe|first5=T.|last6=De Bie|first6=B.|last7=Heikinheimo|first7=O.|last8=Horne|first8=A. W.|last9=Kiesel|first9=L.|access-date=2017-11-07|archive-date=2020-05-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200516040259/https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/24435778|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 手術治療 ===
手術治療能有效減緩症狀、根除惡性腫瘤發生率。

